subject: College Athletics
Football
lead_paragraph: It was not a good week to be a top-five team, as No. 4 L.S.U. was pounded by No. 11 Florida, No. 1 Oklahoma lost to No. 5 Texas and No. 3 Missouri fell to No. 17 Oklahoma State, throwing the rankings into chaos.
